into [foreign language].

00:29:03.330 --> 00:29:06.520
He started performing
as the hip-hop DJ

00:29:06.520 --> 00:29:09.660
and rapper TJ Big Blaster
Electric Boogie.

00:29:09.660 --> 00:29:12.520
His hip-hop parties
attracted large crowds.

00:29:12.520 --> 00:29:15.970
And while he performed
under an official license,

00:29:15.970 --> 00:29:19.640
which you can see here, this
is what they looked like,

00:29:19.640 --> 00:29:23.650 position:56%
