00:29:23.650 --> 00:29:26.750
And I will show that in
his lyrics in a second.

00:29:26.750 --> 00:29:33.500
So his Christian name is Alexander
Morawitz, and he got this license

00:29:33.500 --> 00:29:38.840
for voice singing, not as
a rapper or DJ or whatever.

00:29:38.840 --> 00:29:45.160
And this is a rather late license
from June 1989, he had one already

00:29:45.160 --> 00:29:48.650
in 1984 and 1985, but he had

00:29:48.650 --> 00:29:51.730
to renew it every year,
so this is a later one.

00:29:51.730 --> 00:29:56.880
And he could he was -- he had
got a very high rating, A,

00:29:56.880 --> 00:29:58.180
just like American grades.

00:29:58.180 --> 00:30:04.090
So he got an A. And therefore,
he could receive payments

00:30:04.090 --> 00:30:06.750
from the people who
