00:30:10.790 --> 00:30:12.940
And sometimes his performance
would be five minutes,

00:30:12.940 --> 00:30:15.460
sometimes his performance
would be 20 minutes,

00:30:15.460 --> 00:30:17.300
sometimes they were even longer.

00:30:17.300 --> 00:30:20.380
And he would get money,
and that was true

00:30:20.380 --> 00:30:22.330
for almost every B-Boy crew too.

00:30:22.330 --> 00:30:25.370
So they could make money and
then they invested this money

00:30:25.370 --> 00:30:27.680
into the raw material
to make their clothing

00:30:27.680 --> 00:30:30.450
or to buy records and
so on and so forth.

00:30:30.450 --> 00:30:35.410
So this is Alexander Morawitz, AKA
TJ Big Blaster Electric Boogie.

