00:30:48.930 --> 00:30:51.430
In other words, he could not get
any bigger, because the Palace

00:30:51.430 --> 00:30:52.730
of the Republic was the biggest --

00:30:52.730 --> 00:30:55.530
it was not only the
seat of the government,

00:30:55.530 --> 00:30:58.710
but also it was the biggest
youth club in the GDR.

00:30:58.710 --> 00:31:02.200
And it could not get any more
official, because you had

00:31:02.200 --> 00:31:06.470
to be an officially licensed
artist to perform there.

00:31:06.470 --> 00:31:07.850
So this is it.

00:31:07.850 --> 00:31:12.010
And you can try to decipher the
